(firstQuint)Classification of Periodontitis Revisited: A Cluster Analysis.

 This is a retrospective cross-sectional study based on a prospectively maintained database of consecutive patients attending the Departement of Periodontology at the Rothschild hospital.

 A cluster analysis will help to distinguish clinical and microbiological profils of periodontal patients.

